title: Fort Dupont Park: Schedule Of Events
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Things To Do     Schedule Of Events              Schedule Of Events           Keyword       By Date     Start Date      End Date          Search         Upcoming Events    Showing 1 results    Show ALL instances of recurring events   RSS Feed      Fort Dupont Park  2016 FORT DUPONT SUMMER CONCERT SERIES      Time: 6:00 PM to 9:30 PM Location: FODU Fees: FREE     Saturday, August 20, 2016 FORT DUPONT  View Details                2015 Fort Dupont Summer Concert Series Fort Dupont Activity Center The Fort Dupont Activity Center under the National Park Service will be hosting environmental education programs starting September 12,2015 and held every Saturday until October 3,2015. In order of events, the topics are: Build a Terrarium, Beneficial Insects, Composting Basics and All about Trees. Events are free and open to all ages lasting from  11:00 AM to 1:00 PM at Ft Dupont Park, Washington DC SE 20020. Reservations are required with attendance limited to 20 individuals. For more information, please call 202-426-7723
